      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HUMBLE HERO (2) built on a nice second two starts back at Mackay with success over 1200m at Rockhampton a week-and-a-half ago, getting home by a neck. Natalea Summers scored on him last time and retains the ride. Beautifully placed and is sure to play a major role again. SILENT FOX (1) was sent out favourite but could only finish fifth over 1200m at Nanango last time. Prior to that had been racing well, collecting two minor placings on end. Has the pace to settle in the leading division and will give backers a sight. BELVEDERE MISS (8) turned in a eye-catching run last start over 1200m at Rockhampton, winding up hard from well back on straightening to finish a close second. Will be doing her best work late. HEROIC TALENT (5) turned in a much better effort last time out to score by 1.2 lengths over 1200m at Mackay. Likely to be there at the finish again.",
